{
  "stem": "16930.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were being sent to Czechoslovakia to be trained there, so they were making selections of people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was in that thing there, what they called [NON-ENGLISH], although no pilot training was taking place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mostly we-- most of the day was spent playing volleyball.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You know, so were just hanging around, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then some did get sent to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some were for different reasons ruled out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I never got to be a pilot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was ruled out of there for some reason, fortunately for myself, because I subsequently met another fellow there about a year later on the beach in Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he told me that most of those guys were dead already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Most of the guys on that [NON-ENGLISH] were dead, because that was-- at that-- the kind of planes they had and I don't think they would be allowed to fly under that-- the FF-- the-- America would not allow those planes to fly in America.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You couldn't land at an airport with a lot of those planes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And a lot of them were dead, or seriously injured, if not dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was sorry at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then it was the biggest blow to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- as a kid 19 years old, that's what I wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- but looking back, it was a lucky break.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got a lucky break and I'm still alive today.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So then-- then I was in the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was transferred to the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I was in the air force.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was at an-- a couple of airbases.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was working out of the supply room, putting supply room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were supplies to be issued.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and Ezer Weizman was an officer there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was only a lieutenant there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
